WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.000
SMAI is the Smart Environmental Monitoring System. A web platform for capturing, monitoring, and analyzing environmental data in real time.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Log in with your email and select your role. As an administrator, you access the Dashboard, the system control center.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:32.000
Here you see a general overview: total readings, active sensors, current alerts. Each sensor shows its latest reading and status. The weekly chart helps detect patterns.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:42.000
In Thresholds you configure alert limits for each sensor. Press "+ New threshold", select the parameter, enter minimum and maximum, and save.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:50.000
The system automatically validates readings against these values.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Query historical data with filters by date, parameter, and location. Results are shown in a dynamic table. Export to PDF or Excel with a single click for your reports.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:18.000
The Alerts module records every time a reading exceeds the configured thresholds. You can simulate an alert to test the system.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:35.000
SMAI: actionable data for a sustainable future.
